Just one more note on the tent. issue... I have a friend in Minnesota who is
the third owner of a C42 ( no tent or rack )Westfalia. The original owner
had 5 kids and this Westfalia was purchased with the tent and correct
aluminum brackets. He has talked with the one of  the sons of the original
owner who has confirmed this.

Scott
'67 Westy


